/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.koName: You're getting the hang of it. We just wanted to send you a little something by way of encourangement. Don't let up.
/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.enName: YOU'RE GETTING THE HANG OF IT. WE JUST WANTED TO SEND YOU A LITTLE SOMETHING BY WAY OF ENCOURANGEMENT. DON'T LET UP.

/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.koName: Vallis Fractures: A Token of Appreciation
/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.enName: VALLIS FRACTURES: A TOKEN OF APPRECIATION

/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.koName: You're doing good work, Sparky. At the current rate Smokefinger charts a plateau in seismic activity before long. That's good news for Fortuna. Keep it up.
/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.enName: YOU'RE DOING GOOD WORK, SPARKY. AT THE CURRENT RATE SMOKEFINGER CHARTS A PLATEAU IN SEISMIC ACTIVITY BEFORE LONG. THAT'S GOOD NEWS FOR FORTUNA. KEEP IT UP.

/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.koName: Vallis Fractures: I Think It's Working
/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.enName: VALLIS FRACTURES: I THINK IT'S WORKING

/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.koName: The Vallis is more stable these days, thanks to the work you're doing. But we've still got fractures erupting every day, and until Nef concedes the threat we have to take care of ourselves. Find them. Seal them. We're counting on you.
/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.enName: THE VALLIS IS MORE STABLE THESE DAYS, THANKS TO THE WORK YOU'RE DOING. BUT WE'VE STILL GOT FRACTURES ERUPTING EVERY DAY, AND UNTIL NEF CONCEDES THE THREAT WE HAVE TO TAKE CARE OF OURSELVES. FIND THEM. SEAL THEM. WE'RE COUNTING ON YOU.

/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.koName: I clock 75-plus fractures sealed. I shudder to think what state we'd be in if we didn't have you helping us out like this. Kids are shutting down sound in their racks, knowing you're out there. Thank you.
/lotus/language/messages/orbheisteventre.enName: I CLOCK 75-PLUS FRACTURES SEALED. I SHUDDER TO THINK WHAT STATE WE'D BE IN IF WE DIDN'T HAVE YOU HELPING US OUT LIKE THIS. KIDS ARE SHUTTING DOWN SOUND IN THEIR RACKS, KNOWING YOU'RE OUT THERE. THANK YOU.
